据报道，《28年后》已在东北部开始拍摄https://www.nme.com/news/film/28-years-later-has-reportedly-begun-filming-in-the-north-east-cillian-murphy-3760134?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=28-据报道，几年后已在西里安·墨菲东北部开始拍摄Elizabeth AubreyTue, 28 May 2024 14:17:51 +0000 Film NewsNews https://www.nme.com/?p=3760134 <p><img width="2000" height="1271" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Cillian-Murphy-Photo-by-Sarah-Morris_WireImage.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="希里安·墨菲" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Cillian-Murphy-Photo-by-Sarah-Morris_WireImage.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Cillian-Murphy-Photo-by-Sarah-Morris_WireImage-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Cillian-Murphy-Photo-by-Sarah-Morris_WireImage-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Cillian-Murphy-Photo-by-Sarah-Morris_WireImage-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Cillian-Murphy-Photo-by-Sarah-Morris_WireImage-1392x885.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Cillian-Murphy-Photo-by-Sarah-Morris_WireImage-1068x679.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>该片将由丹尼·博伊尔执导，希里安·墨菲回归</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/28-years-later-has-reportedly-begun-filming-in-the-north-east-cillian-murphy-3760134">据报道，《28 年后》的帖子已在东北部开始拍摄，并</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1271" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Cillian-Murphy-Photo-by-Sarah-Morris_WireImage.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="希里安·墨菲" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Cillian-Murphy-Photo-by-Sarah-Morris_WireImage.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Cillian-Murphy-Photo-by-Sarah-Morris_WireImage-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Cillian-Murphy-Photo-by-Sarah-Morris_WireImage-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Cillian-Murphy-Photo-by-Sarah-Morris_WireImage-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Cillian-Murphy-Photo-by-Sarah-Morris_WireImage-1392x885.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Cillian-Murphy-Photo-by-Sarah-Morris_WireImage-1068x679.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>据<a href="https://theknowledgeonline.com/news/danny-boyle-directs-28-years-later-as-production-begins" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><i>《知识》杂志</i></a>的最新报道<i>，《28 年之后》</i>本周已在东北部开始拍摄。</p><ul><li aria-level="1"><b>阅读更多：</b> <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/film-interviews/28-days-later-interview-anniversary-cillian-murphy-danny-boyle-3340282"><b>《惊变 28 天》20 岁：丹尼·博伊尔和希里安·墨菲讲述为何今天无法制作该剧</b></a></li></ul><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/28-years-later-in-development-danny-boyle-to-direct-3568935">新电影的消息于今年早些时候首次公布</a>，并确认导演<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/danny-boyle">丹尼·博伊尔</a>和编剧亚历克斯·加兰（2002 年原版《<i>惊变 28 天》</i>的导演）将回归该系列电影。 <em>《二十八年后》</em>将是原版电影后续三部曲的第一部。</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/cillian-murphy">希里安·墨菲</a><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/cillian-murphy-to-return-in-danny-boyles-28-years-later-3757490">最近也被证实将重返开启他职业生涯的球队。</a></p><p>本月早些时候，<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/heres-when-28-years-later-is-coming-out-3755617">这部电影的正式上映日期为2025年6月20日</a>。<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/aaron-taylor-reportedly-star-in-28-years-later-3750446">亚伦·泰勒-约翰逊、朱迪·科默、拉尔夫·费因斯</a>和<a href="https://deadline.com/2024/05/jack-oconnell-28-years-later-trilogy-danny-boyle-1235906177/">杰克·奥康奈尔</a>也将与墨菲并肩作战。</p><p>现在， <i>《知识》</i>报道称，这部电影正在东北部的多个地点拍摄，包括诺森伯兰郡。</p><p>索尼电影集团董事长汤姆·罗斯曼（Tom Rothman）最近向<a href="https://deadline.com/2024/05/tom-rothman-streaming-audiences-quentin-tarantino-1235920644/"><i>Deadline</i></a>透露了墨菲的角色，他表示这位演员将以“令人惊讶的方式和成长的方式回归，让我这么说吧”。</p><p>他继续说道：“这是丹尼最好的作品，与非常商业化的类型相结合，就像我们与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/edgar-wright">埃德加·赖特</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/baby-driver-film-review-2095590"><i>极盗车神</i></a>一样。有时，当你将一位真正的招牌导演投入商业舞台时，它会提升它的水平。” </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="惊变 28 天 (2002) 预告片 #1 |电影剪辑经典预告片" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/7suz9ndPBHg?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> 2002 年的<i>《惊变 28 天》中，</i>墨菲扮演自行车快递员吉姆，他从昏迷中醒来，发现一种高度传染性、引发攻击性的病毒的意外释放导致了社会崩溃。</p><p> <i>《28 年后》</i>预计将成为新三部曲的第一部，加兰将担任这三部曲的编剧和制作人。博伊尔预计只会回归第一部，据报道<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/film-reviews/candyman-review-nia-dacosta-horror-3028692"><i>坎迪曼</i></a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/films/the-marvels"><i>漫威</i></a>导演<a href="https://variety.com/2024/film/news/nia-dacosta-director-28-years-later-trilogy-second-installment-1235967039/">尼亚·达科斯塔正在就第二部进行谈判</a>。每部电影的制作预算约为 7500 万美元（5900 万英镑）。</p><p> 2022 年，为<a href="https://www.nme.com/features/film-interviews/28-days-later-interview-anniversary-cillian-murphy-danny-boyle-3340282">庆祝《惊变<i>28 天</i>》上映 20 周年</a>，墨菲和博伊尔在接受<i>《NME》</i>采访时表示，他们经常谈论热门僵尸电影的续作。虽然墨菲说他现在已经太老了，但博伊尔透露，几年前加兰曾写过一部名为<i>《28 个月后》</i>的剧本，但最终没有结果。</p><p>博伊尔当时说道：“我很想（执导这部电影）。实际上感觉这是一段非常美好的时光。有趣的是，我没有想到这一点，直到你说出这句话，我才想起“砰，这个剧本！”这又以英格兰为背景，非常关于英格兰。不管怎样，我们拭目以待……谁知道呢？”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/28-years-later-has-reportedly-begun-filming-in-the-north-east-cillian-murphy-3760134">据报道，《28 年后》的帖子已在东北部开始拍摄，并</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
